%%{init: {'theme':'dark'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    
    participant Caller
    participant Backend as "Signaling Server"
    participant STUN as "STUN/TURN Server"
    participant Callee

    Note over Caller, Callee: 1. Call Initiation & WebRTC Setup
    Caller->>Backend: WSS joinCall(callId)
    Callee->>Backend: WSS joinCall(callId)
    
    Caller->>Caller: Create RTCPeerConnection
    Callee->>Callee: Create RTCPeerConnection
    
    Note over Caller, Backend: 2. Offer & Answer Exchange
    Caller->>Caller: Create Offer (SDP)
    Caller->>Caller: setLocalDescription(Offer)
    Caller->>Backend: WSS send webrtc:offer (SDP)
    Backend->>Callee: WSS relay webrtc:offer
    
    Callee->>Callee: setRemoteDescription(Offer)
    Callee->>Callee: Create Answer (SDP)
    Callee->>Callee: setLocalDescription(Answer)
    Callee->>Backend: WSS send webrtc:answer (SDP)
    Backend->>Caller: WSS relay webrtc:answer
    
    Caller->>Caller: setRemoteDescription(Answer)
    
    Note over Caller, Callee: 3. ICE Candidate Gathering
    Caller->>STUN: Request Public IP/Port
    STUN-->>Caller: Return ICE Candidates
    Caller->>Backend: WSS send webrtc:iceCandidate
    Backend->>Callee: WSS relay webrtc:iceCandidate
    Callee->>Callee: addIceCandidate()
    
    Callee->>STUN: Request Public IP/Port
    STUN-->>Callee: Return ICE Candidates
    Callee->>Backend: WSS send webrtc:iceCandidate
    Backend->>Caller: WSS relay webrtc:iceCandidate
    Caller->>Caller: addIceCandidate()
    
    Note over Caller, Callee: 4. Peer-to-Peer Connection Established
    Caller-->>Callee: Direct Video/Audio Streaming
    Callee-->>Caller: Direct Video/Audio Streaming
